<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.4.4">
<l>taḷaiyaviḻ kōtai mālai yirupālta yaṅka verikāṉṟi raṇṭu taṟukaṇ</l>
<l>aḷaveḻa vemmai mikka variyāki vaṉṟu pariyōṉci ṉaṅka ḷaviḻa</l>
<l>vaḷaiyuki rāḷi moympiṉ maṟavōṉa tākam matiyātu ceṉṟō rukirāl</l>
<l>piḷaveḻa viṭṭa kuṭṭa matuvaiya mūṭu perunīriṉ mummai peritē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As garlands of flowers with closed [buds] opening swayed at both sides,</l>
<l rend="indent">as his two cruel eyes flashing [like] fire opened to their full measure,</l>
<l>Becoming a very fierce lion that day, when the huge demon loosed his ragings,</l>
<l>The pool [of blood] that the lion with curved claws,</l>
<l rend="indent">advancing without [even] thinking, made rise,</l>
<l>With [only] one claw in a slit in the chest of the strong, wrathful one,</l>
<l rend="indent">was threefold greater than the great flood that covered the earth.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
